The,Ozlo,REST,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Ozlo,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,The,API,allows,for,searching,and,retrieving,finding,related,artifacts,and,managing,conversations,Public,documentation,is,not,available,API,access,comes,with,account,service,Ozlo,is,a,knowledge,platform,that,allows,for,intelligent,management,of,data,and,knowledge,for,messaging,searching,bots,and,answers